    "The core of the paper then answers our three research questions.",
    "Section 4 deconstructs the strategies for using LLMs (RQ1).",
    "Section 5 maps the ecosystem of software engineering techniques used to enhance and constrain this engine (RQ2).",
    "Section 6 takes a broader view to examine current technical challenges and identify opportunities for future research (RQ3).",
